{"title":"Ride with Lael Wilcox at the Komoot Rally Events in 2024!","link":"https://theradavist.com/komoot-rally-events-in-2024/","date":1708011196000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/02/405535-202120Women27s20Komoot20Torino20Nice20Rally20E2809420Rugile20Kaladyte20E2809420059-66ba78-original-1635525630.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Lael Wilcox, will again be hosting two komoot Women’s Rally Events in 2024, with applications for the first event, the <a href=\"https://www.komoot.com/collection/2552904/-komoot-women-s-badlands-rally-2024\" target=\"_blank\">komoot Women’s Badlands Rally</a>, now open. Find out more here.<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1535\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?fit=1200,1535&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?resize=1024,786&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?resize=768,589&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?resize=1800,1382&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?resize=1335,1025&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?resize=700,537&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/08/RugileKaladyte_KomootHutTrip_08-.jpg?resize=1536,1179&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Key Takeaways</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>In April 2024 komoot and Lael Wilcox will host the <a href=\"http://email.komoot.com/c/eJxEkLFy5SAMRb8GOt6ABAEVFNv4NzIgePu8a4wHk_Xk73ecFGmPNNK5l1M70vp7f19LJNLkJfd2pP3zBm_-LaDk0d657zPxvCFqIHIuKZ-RlUXMKmVglXUh6zOipyxLrMahD7JG43XQGgiMrC2t233D6ADkPcpXZFezN_npQ0EKxT5z9k9dkmcNbIKVawQNVoNxBo0z9HjqymSwlkQlWCRh9d_eep8P7k1u8TXncQr8JWARsFzX9fgZC1i4b1vlufZdwALOAWkrYFHfS-rqre7qVDmVLe3lVCNt26e6HeQx6nmWzncEQOvRyBH_9NcurJ6vOlJJ_9bz22PGY_Ty8fVIzsijyY-zjq-eES39DwAA__96jnT4\" target=\"_blank\">komoot Women’s Badlands Rally</a>, starting in Granada and finishing in Almería, Spain.</li>\n<li>Komoot Women’s Badlands Rally 2024 is open for applications from the 15th to the 22nd of February.</li>\n<li>The komoot Women’s Rally events aim to connect, unite, and break down the barriers in adventure cycling by making adventures by bike more accessible to women and all who identify as women of all backgrounds.</li>\n<li>Komoot will host two Women’s Rally events in 2024, one in Europe and one in the US – details about Fall (Autumn) 2024 komoot Women’s US Rally will be shared by komoot later in Spring.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img width=\"2666\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/2024_Komoot_Womens_AZ_Rally-21.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/2024_Komoot_Womens_AZ_Rally-21.jpg?w=2666&amp;quality=75 2666w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/2024_Komoot_Womens_AZ_Rally-21.jpg?resize=1200,600&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/2024_Komoot_Womens_AZ_Rally-21.jpg?resize=2000,1000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/2024_Komoot_Womens_AZ_Rally-21.jpg?resize=768,384&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/2024_Komoot_Womens_AZ_Rally-21.jpg?resize=1536,768&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/2024_Komoot_Womens_AZ_Rally-21.jpg?resize=2048,1024&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Check back in tomorrow for a recap of the 2023 Arizona komoot Rally!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/komoot-rally-events-in-2024/\">Ride with Lael Wilcox at the Komoot Rally Events in 2024!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"c902d11e9b3a5bc03d1d561f0c33ebeadc3a7a8b185ef9e6d4b8cf0f7a561a5f","category":"Cycling"}